I really-- I do not want to.

34:33.656 --> 34:36.495
It's not the kind of person
that I am,

34:36.562 --> 34:39.534
in terms of what I want to do,

34:39.601 --> 34:43.074
but if I have to,

34:43.141 --> 34:45.045
if there's just no other way,

34:45.112 --> 34:47.650
and I have to...

34:47.717 --> 34:50.556
do it...

34:50.622 --> 34:52.392
to you...

34:55.132 --> 34:58.404
...how would you want me to...

35:00.976 --> 35:03.949
