35:04.016 --> 35:07.489
about the Frenchman,
the Englishman, and the Jew

35:07.556 --> 35:09.694
who were sentenced to death?

35:09.761 --> 35:13.903
Oh, oh, no... no.

35:13.969 --> 35:16.074
Three men

35:16.140 --> 35:18.111
are sentenced to death,
and they are

35:18.177 --> 35:20.381
told that they can choose

35:20.448 --> 35:22.720
their form of execution.

35:24.323 --> 35:25.859
The Frenchman says,

35:25.926 --> 35:28.365
"I choose the guillotine."

35:28.431 --> 35:30.268
So, they build a guillotine,

35:30.334 --> 35:33.174
and they chop off his head.

35:34.443 --> 35:36.982
The Englishman says,

35:37.048 --> 35:40.288
"I choose the firing squad."

35:40.355 --> 35:42.259
So, they get together
a firing squad,

35:42.326 --> 35:44.463
and they shoot him.

35:46.535 --> 35:48.337
Now, the Jew is left...

35:48.404 --> 35:51.611
I went to see the psychologist
from my high school.

35:53.381 --> 35:56.287
He said that he would be
my therapist,

35:56.354 --> 35:58.625
starting next week.

36:03.434 --> 36:06.140
...and the Jew says,

36:06.207 --> 36:08.377
"Old age."

